The project implements a sports activity coordination platform with three core business domains:

1. Game Management System (Score: 90/100)
- Multi-step game creation with sport-specific validations
- Participant management with timing restrictions
- Weather-integrated outdoor activity planning
- Location-based game discovery and recommendations
- Auto-archive system for completed games

Key files:
```
src/components/GameDetails.tsx
src/components/CreateGame.tsx
src/lib/supabaseService.ts
```

2. Weather Integration System (Score: 85/100)
- Sport-specific weather analysis within 4-hour windows
- Custom outdoor activity suitability algorithms
- Temperature, precipitation, and wind speed thresholds
- Weather-based game recommendations and alerts

Key files:
```
src/lib/weatherService.ts
src/hooks/useGameActions.ts
```

3. Location Services (Score: 80/100)
- Sport venue proximity calculations
- Location-based game matchmaking
- Custom game clustering and visualization
- Dynamic game discovery based on user location
- Sport-specific venue recommendations

Key files:
```
src/components/MapView.tsx
