```

Supporting Systems:

4. User Engagement (Score: 70/100)
- Sport preference matching
- Achievement tracking based on participation
- Multi-step onboarding with sport preferences
- Real-time game notifications and updates

Key files:
```
src/components/Onboarding.tsx
